text: Colin Pinch (23 June 1921 - 17 November 2006) was an Australian cricketer. He played 63 first-class matches for New South Wales and South Australia between 1949/50 and 1959/60. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1921 births Category:2006 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:South Australia cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
